description: Being a Southern California family, the owners of this truck wanted to bring a beach party atmosphere to the streets. So in that spirit, Woody's grill offers up a simple grilled menu that includes some of your favorite dishes such as cheese and mac, grilled shrimp, blackened ahi tuna, grilled white fish, burger sliders, crack dogs, quesadillas, burritos and more. Try a steak salad stuffed with fries! Their specialty dish is chicken crack. It is a shredded chicken recipe with southwest seasonings, black beans and corn all combined and slow cooked together. Put in in your quesadilla, a truck favorite! You can top your nachos or hot dog, or stuff it inside a burrito or tacos! Their guacamole and pico is second to none and made fresh everyday!! They travel all over Los Angeles county so you will be able to catch them soon near you!
name: Woody's Grill
